==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Excuser
<hw>Ex*cus"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
offers excuses or pleads in extenuation of the fault of another.</def>
<rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who excuses or forgives another.</def>
<rj><au>Shelton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Excuss</ent>⟦br⟧
